wikipedia_page.main: John Ayscough Nunn (19 March 1906 – 6 April 1987) was an English first-class cricketer active 1926–46 who played for Middlesex and Oxford University. He was born in Hadley, Barnet, Hertfordshire; died in Colintraive, Argyll.
